02:05:19,544 --> 02:05:20,878
That's wonderful news.

1068
02:05:23,089 --> 02:05:24,215
Do you mind?

1069
02:05:31,556 --> 02:05:32,723
Oliver.
Oliver.

1070
02:05:32,807 --> 02:05:34,809
Oliver.
Hey, hey, hey.

1071
02:05:34,892 --> 02:05:36,252
Darling, when are you coming back?

1072
02:05:36,811 --> 02:05:38,104
I wish I was.

1073
02:05:38,437 --> 02:05:41,858
You caught us in the process of choosing
the new you for next summer.

1074
02:05:42,108 --> 02:05:44,610
And guess what? He's a she.
Oh, no.

1075
02:05:44,694 --> 02:05:47,405
Speaking of she's, I'm calling
to tell you guys I got engaged.

1076
02:05:49,365 --> 02:05:51,492
Wonderful!

1077
02:05:51,576 --> 02:05:53,452
Congratulations.
Mazel tov!

1078
02:05:53,536 --> 02:05:55,681
Congratulations, Oliver.
Thank you, thank you, thank you.

1079
02:05:55,705 --> 02:05:59,083
Listen, we'll leave you...
We'll let you speak to Elio.

1080
02:05:59,292 --> 02:06:01,377
Happy Hanukkah!
Happy Hanukkah!

1081
02:06:01,460 --> 02:06:02,587
Bye, sweetheart.

1082
02:06:10,344 --> 02:06:11,762
They know about us.

1083
02:06:13,222 --> 02:06:14,390
I figured.

1084
02:06:16,851 --> 02:06:18,102
How?

1085
02:06:19,854 --> 02:06:21,731
Well, from the way your dad spoke to me.

1086
02:06:23,149 --> 02:06:25,067
He made me feel
like I was a part of the family.

1087
02:06:25,651 --> 02:06:26,944
Almost like a son-in-law.

1088
02:06:29,155 --> 02:06:30,281
You're so lucky.

1089
02:06:31,866 --> 02:06:34,660
My father would have carted me off
to a correctional facility.

1090
02:06:37,205 --> 02:06:38,456
Elio.

1091
02:06:42,084 --> 02:06:46,130
Elio. Elio. Elio. Elio.
Elio. Elio. Elio. Elio.

1092
02:06:49,800 --> 02:06:51,302
Oliver.

1093
02:06:54,180 --> 02:06:55,723
I remember everything.

1094
02:11:00,593 --> 02:11:01,886
Elio.

1095
02:11:04,138 --> 02:11:05,139
Elio.

